xt","text":"Were they ashamed when they acted so detestably?"},{"kind":"text","text":" They weren’t at all ashamed."},{"kind":"text","text":" They can no longer feel humiliation. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jr 3:3","book":"Jer","chapter":3,"verse":3,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jr 8:12","book":"Jer","chapter":8,"verse":12,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" Therefore, they will fall among the fallen."},{"kind":"text","text":" When I punish them, they will collapse, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jr 8:10–12","book":"Jer","chapter":8,"verse":10,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" says the "},{"kind":"text","text":"Lord","style":"divine"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Jr 3:3","book":"Jer","chapter":3,"verse":3},{"label":"Jr 8:12","book":"Jer","chapter":8,"verse":12},{"label":"Jr 8:10–12","book":"Jer","chapter":8,"verse":10}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jer:6:16","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"This is what the "},{"kind":"text","text":"Lord","style":"divine"},{"kind":"text","text":" says:"},{"kind":"text","text":" Stand by the roadways and look."},{"kind":"text","text":" Ask about the ancient paths, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Is 59:8","book":"Isa","chapter":59,"verse":8,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jr 18:15","book":"Jer","chapter":18,"verse":15,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jb 24:13","book":"Job","chapter":24,"verse":13,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Pr 8:20","book":"Pro","chapter":8,"verse":20,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Pr 12:28","book":"Pro","chapter":12,"verse":28,"letter":"e"},{"kind":"text","text":" “Which is the way to what is good?”"},{"kind":"text","text":" Then take it"},{"kind":"text","text":" and find rest for yourselves. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 11:29","book":"Mat","chapter":11,"verse":29,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" But they protested, “We won’t!”"}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Is 59:8","book":"Isa","chapter":59,"verse":8},{"labe